Recursion Practice Questions:
Factorial Calculation: Write a recursive function to compute the factorial of a given number n.

Fibonacci Sequence: Write a recursive function to find the nth Fibonacci number.

Sum of Digits: Write a recursive function to calculate the sum of digits of a given integer n.

Power Function: Implement a recursive function to compute a^b (i.e., a raised to the power of b).

Reverse a String: Write a recursive function to reverse a given string.

Check Palindrome: Write a recursive function to check whether a given string is a palindrome.

Greatest Common Divisor (GCD): Implement a recursive function to compute the GCD of two numbers.

Tower of Hanoi: Write a recursive function to solve the Tower of Hanoi problem for n disks.

Count Ways to Climb Stairs: There are n stairs, and you can climb 1 or 2 steps at a time. Write a recursive function to count the number of ways to reach the nth stair.

Generate All Subsets of a String: Write a recursive function to generate all subsets (power set) of a given string.
